25
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:38,110
that hardware is where we have
the real or physical resources.

26
00:01:38,110 --> 00:01:42,490
We're going to run an operating
system to control access to those

27
00:01:42,490 --> 00:01:47,040
hardware resources, and those resources
then are going to be made available to

28
00:01:47,040 --> 00:01:49,920
the various applications that we have.

